<LP>
   LONDON -- Fisons PLC, a British pharmaceuticals and
laboratory-equipment maker, said it will take a controlling
interest in a Japanese-based joint venture with Fujisawa
Pharmaceutical Co.
   Fujisawa has agreed to sell Fisons a 15% stake in
Fujisawa-Fisons KK, Fisons said. The purchase will lift
Fisons's holding to 65%.
</LP>
