                              Jun 28    Jun 27      Year
                                                                                                       

   U.S. ......................  330.8   328.5     +  1.8
   Britain ...................  703.1   707.2     -  2.5
   Canada ....................  388.2   386.9     - 10.2
   Japan ..................... 1309.7  1318.7     - 20.9
   France ....................  570.3   570.4     +  0.6
   Germany ...................  307.0   303.2     +  7.6
